  "name": "RPlog_Coming_Unglued",
  "title": "Coming Unglued on Selene",
  "summary": "On the domed Imperial starport of Selene, the off-duty TIE pilot Krieg Inrokana, simmering with barely-controlled rage over the Jedi, clashes with the veteran pilot Jal'Dana Rall as she stargazes on a bench. Their confrontation escalates into a tense exchange about order, the greater good, and the futility he feels at being unable to defeat the Jedi, with Krieg threatening to carve out the heart of the Jedi Ai'kani. Rall, revealing herself as his superior Lt Commander Rall, coolly absorbs his fury, orders him to stay away from the Jedi and report sightings, and warns that blind rage makes him a danger to his squadron. As Grand Admiral Danik Kreldin passes obliviously nearby on his own inspection, Seifer Wolf arrives and Rall smoothly defuses the scene, leaving with quiet concern that Krieg may crack under pressure.",
